snippet.title: Alien Attack - MSX-BASIC - MSX Computer Magazine - 1986
snippet.description:
A simple shooter game written by L. Dorsman and published in MSX Computer Magazine issue 7 in 1986.

Quite a tricky A.I. these aliens have...

This game is not too good, but became mostly famous because it was on the cover of the great MSX Listingboek, published by MSX Computer Magazine, with only their program listings in it, including this one.

Recorded with openMSX.
